    "name": "Brew 炼金学院物语",
    "steam_appid": 1793330,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Brew》是一款结合快节奏战斗与策略的肉鸽游戏，考验玩家在激烈战斗中的反应与资源分配能力。玩家可使用直观的合成系统来炼制多种药水，应对炼金试炼中的各种挑战！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793330/extras/4fe2ecf9d3baa5a87beeb746871e52c6.avif?t=1770309938\" width=800 height=71 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在战斗中收集素材并将它们炼成强力药水，并使用它们来挑战难度逐层提升的试炼之塔！你能喝下药水来强化自己、投掷药水来改变战局，或是装入武器中来强化药水枪！熟悉药水的各种能力，组合出强大连招，成为真正的炼金宗师吧！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793330/extras/81fdc5a7d6f7f955cad765a433d40b0a.poster.avif?t=1770309938\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793330/extras/81fdc5a7d6f7f955cad765a433d40b0a.webm?t=1770309938\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793330/extras/0f0858c0f3fa5fd7af78b5138e130aaa.avif?t=1770309938\" width=800 height=71 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁上百种独特徽章、学习新的药水配方，并创造属于你的独特打法！游戏中有琳琅满目的药水升级、角色技能以及隐藏在试炼之塔中的秘密房间等着你来探索，丰富内容将让你彻底化身为炼金学徒，体验课后成长的喜悦，学会全新的能力！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793330/extras/5936a0516df27fbde2c60cba157a5758.poster.avif?t=1770309938\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793330/extras/5936a0516df27fbde2c60cba157a5758.webm?t=1770309938\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793330/extras/5936a0516df27fbde2c60cba157a5758.mp4?t=1770309938\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793330/extras/6a47755dd3bcc3c8b8f04bf7cd1b3908.avif?t=1770309938\" width=800 height=75 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >和同学、老师们交谈、送他们礼物，或是陪他们一起度过悠闲的时光来培养感情吧！交朋友可是体验学生生活的关键！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793330/extras/9d0e578c26791186ce21185f04e77e3b.poster.avif?t=1770309938\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793330/extras/9d0e578c26791186ce21185f04e77e3b.webm?t=1770309938\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793330/extras/9d0e578c26791186ce21185f04e77e3b.mp4?t=1770309938\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
